CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Anebulo Pharmaceuticals Inc is a clinical-stage biotechnology company. It is developing novel solutions for people suffering from cannabinoid overdose and substance addiction. The product candidate, ANEB-001, is intended to reverse the negative effects of cannabinoid overdose within 1 hour of administration. The signs and symptoms of cannabinoid overdose range from profound sedation to anxiety and panic to psychosis with hallucinations.
